body.description: The innovative Smart Compliance program redefines first aid with two powerful components, innovative cabinet design and the SmartTag refill system, creating the most comprehensive first aid solution available today. The 150 person, XL metal Smart Compliance ANSI B+ food service cabinet without over the counter medication is perfect for an individual restaurant or restaurant chain locations. The unique cabinet design eliminates disorganized and missing supplies, while the clearly labeled compartments create a cabinet that is easy to use and restock. The bottom shelf and door shelves allows you to customize your cabinet to meet your specific needs. The Smart Compliance cabinet SmartTag refill System is a simple but effective way for reordering and restocking, revolutionizing the replenishment process. It is quick, easy, and cost effective. As supplies are used, Smart Tab refill reminder tabs notify you when it is time to reorder supplies and puts reorder information at your fingertips. The solid steel case comes with a carrying handle and can be mounted on a wall or other flat vertical surface.
